Afeitado y ley de Moore
Una pequeña broma acerca de la Ley de Moore y el afeitado: <a href="http://www.economist.com/science/displaystory.cfm?story_id=5624861">A Moore's law for razor blades?</a>.

<blockquote>
For the most cynical shavers, this evolution is mere marketing. Twin blades seemed plausible. Three were a bit unlikely. Four, ridiculous. And five seems beyond the pale.
</blockquote>

¿Alguien se atreve con el afeitado 2.0?

Visto en <a href="http://slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=06/10/26/1936250">Moore's Law For Razor Blades?</a>.


